title: Mother Simulator: Family Life

container.value: 112 North Curry Street, Carson City, NV 89703

creator: Skytec Games, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Become a great housewife in this simulator of mother and family life! Combine housekeeping, cooking, baby caring. Make all your virtual family happy and satisfied!

Keep your house clean and cozy. Chat with guests and treat them with strawberry cakes or slices of hot pizza. M-m-m, delicious! Take care of the baby as exemplary mother: feed from milk bottle, change diapers, bring toys to play with. Other words, enjoy the motherhood and make your baby calm and happy.

Open new doors and rooms in your house, where your virtual family can live. Explore and discover new ways to interact with family members.

This game is not a simple mother simulator, where you care about your baby only in an empty house. Here you can find more characters that need you and your assistance! Day after day you will face new activities, duties, funny situations and more. Will you handle with multitasking of mother’s everyday life?

Customize your baby’s appearance the way you like. We have plenty of hairstyles and colors, baby clothes and skins so feel free to experiment and have fun!

Participate in weekly challenges with unique rewards, where you will test your skills, prove you are worthy of the title “Cool and clever mother” and make your virtual family be proud of you. We will be happy to hear about your achievements in mother simulator challenges!

Meet your husband after a day of hard work, make him feel comfortable and beloved. Pet your dog. Listen to the music. Eat sushi or fresh fruits. Play. Make yourself a cup of coffee. Get angry when everything is going out of control, make another cup of coffee after calming down. Be concentrated, be lazy, be happy mother or be a devil mother. These are your rules, your virtual world and your virtual family!

What do we offer in “Housewife: Mother Simulator” game:
- Tons of baby skins and baby clothes;
- Fancy jewels for mother;
- Sensitive baby according to your actions – baby is upset when you do something wrong and baby is happy when you are an awesome mother;
- Big virtual family with their own needs and dreams;
- Simulator of mother duties and activities – prepare yourself for a true family life;
- Weekly challenges with unique rewards and more.
descriptionShort: This game is the most realistic simulator of mother’s life!

title: Mother Simulator: Happy Virtual Family Life

container.value: 112 North Curry Street, Carson City, NV 89703

creator: Skytec Games, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
9 months of pregnancy have flown by, and it's time to say "Welcome baby"! After giving birth to your newborn baby you could try to be a sweet mommy. Carry out your daily child and pet care duties and receive well-deserved awards.
Now you can become a great mom and housewife with our virtual simulator. Play, have fun with cool character animations and interesting tasks.
You can become a great mother of a newborn baby, and your whole virtual family will be happy! Imagine that your baby can say: “I live”.

Don't forget to invite guests and feed them sweet strawberry cake, be the best housewife! Your child's father is an exemplary family man and a dream dad who takes care of your family and helps to look after your baby. Give your baby the best childhood memories of parents! Having a baby is a big responsibility. Maternity could be an interesting and exciting process with “idle” life simulator! Daycare become a fascinating adventure that children and adults alike.

Open new locations in your house, where your virtual family can live. Explore and discover new ways to interact with family members. Say welcome to baby and new friends and get a virtual pet. You can feel yourself like a wonderful mom and deal with daily duties easily. Cook your tasty breakfast and make dad happy, look after your child and help him to grow happy.
Every day you will get a new list of to-do’s and different tasks. Find out what it means to have a child and have time to take care of him and your pet. We make babysitting an addictive game for kids, teens and adults. Take care of your whole family and help them get happier.

You could play babies games with Mother Simulator: Happy Virtual Family Life everywhere! It’s a perfect vacation to do game. Being a mom in our game is really cool.
Participate in weekly challenges with unique rewards, where you will test your skills, prove you are worthy of the title “Cool and clever mother” and make your virtual family be proud of you. We will be happy to hear about your achievements in mother simulator challenges!

What we offer in “Mother Simulator: Happy Virtual Family Life” game:
- Tons of skins and clothes;
- Fancy jewels for mother;
- Sensitive characters according to your actions;
- Big virtual family with their own needs and dreams;
- Simulator of mother duties and activities – prepare yourself for a true family life;
- Weekly challenges with unique rewards and more.

Tell your happy family story!
descriptionShort: This is a realistic new game of a mom’s daily cares! Manage your house. Play now

title: Mother Simulator: Happy Virtual Family Life

container.value: 112 North Curry Street, Carson City, NV 89703

creator: Skytec Games, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the fascinating world of motherhood with our mother simulator game! Having a baby is a difficult task. Since your happy pregnancy is over you have to manage family life. Enjoy the best 3d simulator among other baby care games.

This game is a realistic simulator in a dream house. Do your everyday family duties and get well-deserved awards. Will you handle with multitasking of mother’s and housewives’ everyday life? Take care of your newborn child and hurry up until your time is over.

Enjoy the most fun baby care game you’ll ever play! Take on the role of mommy in this life simulator game. Now you can become a great mom and be a wonderful housewife at the same time! Deal with house chores, cook, clean, take care of your own pet and don’t forget about your sweet child! Motherhood is tough with this routine.

👪 What are daily mum and dad chores? Play our mother simulator family life game to find out!

👶 Take Care of baby. Feed the infant to make him grow up quickly! Change baby’s stinky diapers, wash your virtual baby, and later put the child to bed.
🏡 Look after your dream house! Take care of pets and babies, clean, cook, and invite your neighbors!
🐕 Take care of your own pet! Feed, wash and walk with it There are numerous missions like pet care, don't miss them!
👫Walk in the garden and chat with neighbors! Feed your guests a strawberry cake, make coffee for neighbors and live your family life to the fullest!
🎀 Mum and dad have to take care of their infant properly! Don’t forget to complete an everyday list of to-dos and different tasks.
🏰Take care of baby and open new locations in your house, where your newborn virtual baby, mum and dad can live.
🤱 Express your love for children and reveal mom skills with a mother life simulator…The newborn baby’s demands are great! So, hurry to play the family life game.

Having a baby is a big responsibility. Don’t waste time and you’ll be able to make your virtual family happy. Take care of baby and find out what motherhood is like! Take on the role of mommy in this raise a family simulator game. Now your 9 months of happy pregnancy is over and it’s time to give your infant the best childhood. Raise a family with our mother simulator family life! The best among baby care games.

Features of Mother Simulator game :

⦁ Realistic environment of Dream House.
⦁ Smooth & Easy controls to use in mother life simulator.
⦁ Colorful design 3D, amazing skins and fancy clothes
⦁ Variety of Tasks & Challenges to experience motherhood!
⦁ Different Missions to Unlock!
⦁ Daycare & household activities to look after babies
⦁ Full experience of having a baby

What are you waiting for? Play mother simulator family life game to become the best!

title: Mother Simulator: Happy Virtual Family Life

container.value: 112 North Curry Street, Carson City, NV 89703

creator: Skytec Games, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the fascinating world of motherhood with our mother simulator game! Having a baby is a difficult challenge. As a mommy and a wife, you have to manage happy family life. Look after the child, feed the baby, do the house cleaning, and experience being a mom. Enjoy the best wife simulator game!

Do your everyday housewife duties and get well-deserved awards. Look after your newborn child and hurry up, the time is limited!

Immerse yourself in the funniest world of your virtual family! Take on the role of mommy in this housewife simulator game. Now you can become a great mom and a first-rate housewife at the same time! Deal with house chores, cook, clean, and don’t forget about your virtual baby! Motherhood is learning about strengths you didn’t know you had...

👪 What are daily mommy and daddy chores? Play our mother simulator family life game to find it out!

👶Look after your child. Feed the baby to make him grow up quickly! Change stinky diapers, wash your newborn baby, and later put the child to bed. Pay attention to the hygiene and cleanliness of your infant. If you think your child's bored, give him a toy or a pacifier, but don't forget to wash it beforehand.

🏡 Look after your dream house! You have no idea how much effort is required to keep the house clean. What does a housewife do all day? House cleaning, cooking, laundry, shopping, gardening, caring for the newborn child, and walking with a pet. Maintain cleanliness at home: clean, renovate, modify space depending on the current needs. Being a mom is tough with all this routine.

🙋‍♀️Make Friends. Walk in the garden to chat with the neighbors! Feed guests a strawberry cake, make coffee for your husband, and live your family life to the fullest in this wife simulator game!

✅Mum and dad have to look after of their virtual baby properly! Don’t forget to complete an everyday list of to-dos and different tasks. This is a task-based game. Every level has a variety of tasks to complete, with the completion of every level a variety of tasks increases. With this baby care game, you'll learn how to make your child happy.

🏰Explore new locations in your house, where your virtual baby, mommy and daddy can live. Play the wife simulator game and open new levels to unlock the dining room and bathroom.

The kid’s demands are so great! So, hurry to play this newborn baby care game. Having a baby is a big responsibility. Express your love for children and reveal mom skills with this mother life simulator game…Mommy and daddy don’t waste time, they make their virtual family happy. Look after your infant and find out what motherhood is like! Show the world that you have the guts to take on the role of a mommy.

Features of Mother Simulator game :
⦁ The realistic environment of YOUR dream house.
⦁ Smooth & Easy controls to use in a mother life simulator.
⦁ Colorful design 3D, skins, and fancy clothes for mommy and her newborn
⦁ Variety of Tasks & Challenges to experience motherhood!
⦁ Different Missions and locations to Unlock!
⦁ Housewife duty activities to look after babies and a dog pet
⦁ All the experience of having a baby and being a mom...
⦁ The best among other baby care games

Mother Simulator is a first-person game. At each stage, a young mum must do everything necessary for her lovely kid, for example, feed, change the diaper or make a child sleep.

What are you waiting for? It's time to give your virtual baby the best childhood. Play a mother simulator family life game to become the best mom!
descriptionShort: Play happy virtual family life, take care of baby and experience housewife duty

Immerse yourself in the funniest world of your virtual family! Take on the role of mommy in this housewife simulator game. Now you can become a great mom and a first-rate housewife at once! Do household chores, cook, clean, and much more. Motherhood is about learning about strengths that you had not known existed.

👪 What are daily mommy and daddy chores? Play Mother Simulator to find it out!

🦸‍♀️ Be a multitasking mom - not skip bath time, sleep, and feed time. Do your everyday real mother and housewife duties to get well-deserved rewards. Hurry up - time is limited!

🏡 Look after your dream house! What does a housewife do all day? House cleaning, cooking, laundry, shopping, gardening, and walking with a pet. Maintain cleanliness at home: clean, renovate, modify space depending on the current needs. Being a mom is a difficult task with all this routine.

🙋‍♀️Make Friends. Walk in the garden to chat with the neighbors. Feed guests a strawberry cake, make coffee for your husband, and live your family life to the fullest in this wife simulator game!

✅Mum and dad have to look after the happiness of their virtual family! Check and complete an everyday list of to-dos and different tasks. It is a task-based game. Every level has a variety of tasks to do. The variation of tasks increases with the completion of every level.

🏰Explore new locations in your family house, where your virtual family can live. Play the wife simulator game and open new levels to unlock the dining room and bathroom.

Hurry to play this life simulator game. Challenge yourself and reveal mom skills with this mother life simulator. Mommy and daddy waste time never. They make their virtual family happy. Join the best moms right now!

Features of Mother Simulator game:
⦁ The realistic environment of your dream house.
⦁ Smooth & Easy controls to use in a mother life simulator.
⦁ Colorful design 3D, various skins, and fancy clothes for mommy.
⦁ Variety of Tasks & Challenges to experience motherhood!
⦁ Different Missions and locations to Unlock!
⦁ Housewife duty activities.

Mother Simulator is a first-person game. A young mother must do everything necessary for her beloved family at every level of the game. Experience all the happiness of motherhood for yourself!

What are you waiting for? It's time to give your virtual family the best life. Play Mother Simulator - the happy family life game to become the best mom!

Immerse yourself in the funniest world of your virtual family! Take on the role of mommy in this housewife simulator game. Now you can become a great mom and a first-rate housewife at once! Do household chores, cook, clean, and much more. Motherhood is about learning about strengths that you had not known existed.

👪 What are daily mommy and daddy chores? Play Mother Simulator to find it out!

🦸‍♀️ Be a multitasking mom - not skip bath time, sleep, and feed time. Do your everyday real mother and housewife duties to get well-deserved rewards. Hurry up - time is limited!

🏡 Look after your dream house! What does a housewife do all day? House cleaning, cooking, laundry, shopping, gardening, and walking with a pet. Maintain cleanliness at home: clean, renovate, modify space depending on the current needs. Being a mom is a difficult task with all this routine.

🙋‍♀️Make Friends. Walk in the garden to chat with the neighbors. Feed guests a strawberry cake, make coffee for your husband, and live your family life to the fullest in this wife simulator game!

✅Mum and dad have to look after the happiness of their virtual family! Check and complete an everyday list of to-dos and different tasks. It is a task-based game. Every level has a variety of tasks to do. The variation of tasks increases with the completion of every level.

🏰Explore new locations in your family house, where your virtual family can live. Play the wife simulator game and open new levels to unlock the dining room and bathroom.

Hurry to play this life simulator game. Challenge yourself and reveal mom skills with this mother life simulator. Mommy and daddy waste time never. They make their virtual family happy. Join the best moms right now!

Features of Mother Simulator game:
⦁ The realistic environment of your dream house.
⦁ Smooth & Easy controls to use in a mother life simulator.
⦁ Colorful design 3D, various skins, and fancy clothes for mommy.
⦁ Variety of Tasks & Challenges to experience motherhood!
⦁ Different Missions and locations to Unlock!
⦁ Housewife duty activities.

Mother Simulator is a first-person game. A young mother must do everything necessary for her beloved family at every level of the game. Experience all the happiness of motherhood for yourself!

What are you waiting for? It's time to give your virtual family the best life. Play Mother Simulator - the happy family life game to become the best mom!
descriptionShort: Play virtual happy mom and dad and be a great housewife in the life simulator.
